  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nAs we enabled WAKU mode by default in 7 RC v1.2 - after upgrade you will see endless spinner and can't use app until manual restarting.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\napp is logged out, should login again\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nendless \"Connecting\"\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Install v1.1\r\n- Enable \"Save password\"\r\n- Install RC 7\r\n- Open app\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version:[RC 7 ](https://ci.status.im/job/status-react/job/release/job/release%252F1.2.x/7/artifact/StatusIm-200330-090900-975b74-release-universal.apk)\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (if on Android please replicate bug whilst running adb logcat)\r\n[Status.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/4402140/Status.log)\r\n\r\n",
